p.k: Gumball and Darwin are offended when Mom calls them “procrastinators”, once she’s told them what it means. / Mum has forced Dad to install a password on the computer… / It's Mother's Day, and Gumball and Darwin discover that Tobias and Banana Joe have both made a card for "The Best Mum in the World". / Darwin starts sneezing repeatedly and it seems he can't stop. / Gumball jaywalks and is pulled over by Donut Cop. / Gumball confronts Clayton about his fabled Seven Pressure Point Heart Exploding Technique, assuming it’s another one of his outlandish claims. / Gumball and Darwin help Rocky land an office job so that his dad, Mr Robinson, will be proud of him. / Gumball and Darwin start noticing small details around Elmore High that don't add up. / When Gumball and Darwin discover his diploma is fake, Principal Brown is determined to keep their discovery a secret.
